{
  "stem": "17135.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 273.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Whenever you saw a-- a-- an SS guard coming to you to beat you up, you rolled to the other side, and-- and-- to let him pick somebody else.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "As a result of this sport, there were, out of the 67 that we were, at least 15 that couldn't walk anymore and-- and three that were dead.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They got heart attacks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were beaten.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were elderly people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were people 40, 50, 60 years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got the first taste what really life in concentration camp is and-- and the lies that-- that Rudolf Hoss told us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We know that is the way a concentration camp and all the actions of the Nazis operate-- deception, deception, deception.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They use words that have a general meaning, but to them it means something else altogether.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was just a cover-up for literally murdering us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now in Sachsenhausen, let me put it this way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had no gas chambers there yet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was early.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They killed the Jews by chicanery, by hard work, and by giving very little food-- maybe 1,200 calories a day.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We got twice a day a water soup that was dishwater soup, we got a quarter of a bread, and some coffee, and that's all.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were no vitamins.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in no time, everybody got sick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We got abscesses all over, all over the body, because the-- the-- and-- and Jews were not-- there was a two blocks-- barracks-- they called this [NON-ENGLISH], they call this in German-- sick barracks, where Germans were treated.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know how well they were treated, but they got some medicine, primitive medicine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Jews were not allowed even to go there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I tell you-- I tell you what my luck was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was very young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was only 15.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
